          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-1" n="1">Beneath this verdant hillock lies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-2" n="2">Demar y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi>. wealthy, &amp; y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> wise:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-5" n="5">His heirs, that he might safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-6" n="6">Have put his carcase in a chest;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-7" n="7">The very chest in which they say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-8" n="8">His other half, his money lay;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-9" n="9">And if his heirs continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-10" n="10">To that dear self he left behind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-11" n="11">I dare believe that four in five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-967O-line-12" n="12">Will think his better half alive.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
